{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":105,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"天网恢恢，疏而不漏，这两个魔头终究还是落到我手上。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":6,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","text":"你真的还要我费事动手吗？盏茶之内，你兄弟两人若不立刻自决，恐怕就要死得更惨了！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":11,"line_start":32,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","text":"姓焦的，我要是你，就趁早跳往海水里。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":11,"line_start":56,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","text":"可是我还是给你一条生路，只要你将你弟弟点上百会穴，抛到我这艘船上来，任凭我处置，我就再给你些食粮清水，让你逃走。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":11,"line_start":60,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"天残焦化","listener":"char_mi_mi","text":"咪咪，十几年来，要是没有妳大哥我，妳早就在孤岛上饿死了，哼！想不到妳现在却来这样报答我？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"天残焦化","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"姓辛的小子，你不用耀武扬威，现在站在你身侧的女人，是我姓焦的养大的，你坐的这条船，是我姓焦的制造的，你算得了甚么东西？你有甚么资格敢在我面前卖狂？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":70,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"天残焦化","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"姓辛的，你这算甚么英雄好汉？你要报仇，就得凭着真本事和我姓焦的见一见高低，你这样算得了甚么报仇？哼！想不道辛鹏九那等英雄，却生出你这种不争气的儿子，除了倚仗别人之外，自己连一点本事也没有，你简直是个懦夫！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":82,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"天残焦化","listener":"char_mi_mi","text":"咪咪，大哥我对妳哪点不好？妳现在这样对我，妳……","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":90,"line_end":92}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xin_jie","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":2,"line_end":8,"text":"辛捷已将行船的性能多多少少了解了一些"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","type":"宿敌","intensity":95,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"仇深似海，新仇旧恨涌上心头"},{"action":"update","target":"char_mi_mi","type":"恋人","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"海上同行，情感渐深"}]},{"id":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":28,"line_end":54,"text":"天残焦化心里翻涌着千百种滋味"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xin_jie","type":"宿敌","intensity":90,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"被仇人追逼，心生恐惧与嫉恨"},{"action":"update","target":"char_mi_mi","type":"主仆","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"对咪咪背叛感到愤怒"}]},{"id":"char_mi_mi","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":24,"line_end":26,"text":"咪咪也知道这原因"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xin_jie","type":"恋人","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"温柔依偎，关心辛捷情绪"}]}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":106,"line_end":190,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mi_mi","speaker_name":"咪咪","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"捷哥哥，我们先把他们救起来吧，他们……他们在岛上的石屋里，还为我们留下一半食物哩，我……我不忍看到他们这副样子。","tone":"恳求","chapter":11,"line_start":106,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","text":"姓焦的，今天你不死在我掌下，就是我死在你掌下！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":152,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","text":"姓焦的，你自己可跑上船来了，可是你弟弟呢？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":11,"line_start":180,"line_end":182}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":124,"line_end":165,"text":"天残焦化朝两丈开外的海船上窜去，与辛捷交手"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_fei_jiao_lao","type":"亲属","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"弟弟落海身亡，悲痛欲绝"}]},{"id":"char_tian_fei_jiao_lao","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":172,"line_end":172,"text":"天废焦劳早也落入万丈洪涛里了"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","type":"亲属","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"覆舟落海而亡"}]},{"id":"char_mi_mi","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":140,"line_end":144,"text":"咪咪正垂着头玩弄着衣袖，以奇异力道托开辛捷"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","type":"主仆","intensity":45,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"暗中出手阻止辛捷攻击焦化"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":191,"line_end":320,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mi_mi","speaker_name":"咪咪","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"他被你打死了吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_mi_mi","speaker_name":"咪咪","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"你没有打死他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_mi_mi","speaker_name":"咪咪","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"捷哥哥，你真好，不但我感激你，他也会感激你的。以前他要是对你做了不好的事，以后他一定会终生后悔，这样岂不是比杀了他要好得多？你假如杀了他，反而变得你不好了。","tone":"温柔","chapter":11,"line_start":224,"line_end":228},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"他们现在怎么样了呢？他们都在想我吧？唉……我是在想他们呀！","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":314,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_xin_jie","speaker_name":"辛捷","listener":"char_mi_mi","text":"那里就是我们的家，我们已经快回家了。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":11,"line_start":318,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_mi_mi","speaker_name":"咪咪","listener":"char_xin_jie","text":"捷哥哥！你看，那是甚么？","tone":"好奇","chapter":11,"line_start":304,"line_end":306}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xin_jie","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":302,"line_end":302,"text":"辛捷向着西天的彩霞跪了下来，默祷父母在天之灵安息"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","type":"宿敌","intensity":70,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"仇恨渐消，转为怜悯"},{"action":"update","target":"char_mi_mi","type":"恋人","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"共患难后情感升温，依偎而行"}]},{"id":"char_mi_mi","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":210,"line_end":228,"text":"咪咪劝辛捷不要杀焦化，说出至深哲理"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xin_jie","type":"恋人","intensity":85,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"以善良感动辛捷，情感进一步深化"},{"action":"update","target":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","type":"主仆","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"为焦化求情，心怀感恩"}]},{"id":"char_tian_can_jiao_hua","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":198,"line_end":198,"text":"天残焦化伏在船舷上呜呜地哭了起来"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xin_jie","type":"宿敌","intensity":60,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"失去斗志，伏船痛哭"}]}]}
